{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bat Bots is a retro shooter that brings the feel of 80s arcades right to your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stun the Bats</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stun the latest prototypes of robotic bats that have escaped into the gloomy forest surrounding your secret lab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/stun.gif?t=1732511196\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize Your Player</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a variety of crosshair designs and colors. Enter your initials to make your mark on the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/custom.gif?t=1732511196\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stun with Friends and Family</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">NOTE: Local Multiplayer Requires At Least One Controller. Multiplayer is NOT supported with ONLY a Mouse &amp; Keyboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with your friends and family as you compete to get the highest score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/comp.gif?t=1732511196\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or work together to defend your top-secret lab before the Bat Bots escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/defense.gif?t=1732511196\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Power-Up with Modifiers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhance your gameplay by shooting the Power Cores dropped by Mod Bats. Once stunned, these cores grant a limited-time modifier that can turn the tide of the game and offer unique advantages in any game mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it